Jeff is an IRS Enrolled Agent, which allows him to practice representation in United States Tax Court.
As a husband and father of 2 girls and 2 boys, raising a family is the most important aspect of Jeff’s life.  Jeff is also a sports enthusiast who enjoys playing ice hockey and golf.





 



