Here's our Story. We're looking forward to hearing yours.
Alliance Wealth Management Group, LLC was formed with a singular focus:  To help people nearing retirement or already in retirement plan their financial future.  We call it income planning, and we specifically create an Alliance Income Plan for each client.  It takes a collaborative effort with our clients to produce a financial plan where the focus remains squarely on what you want to accomplish with your money.

Some of what we do is art; some is science.  Products and strategies vary because family financial situations vary.  We don’t believe that a cookie cutter approach works, therefore, each plan is customized.  We use a variety of insurance and investment products to diversify our client's assets to keep them on the path of financial independence. 

Mike Ballard has been in the financial industry for the past 32 years.  He had an accomplished career at Protective Life Corporation, serving as President/CEO of ProEquities, Inc., a registered broker/dealer.  He built that firm from a start-up to one with 1,100 financial planners around the country.  Mike also served for a number of years on The Children’s Hospital of Alabama Foundation Board of Directors.  In addition, he served as the board’s President and was also appointed to The Hospital’s Board of Trustees.  

After a long career with Protective Life, Mike chose to create Alliance Wealth Management Group, a dozen years ago.  He saw that near-retirees lacked the necessary direction to make their retirement dreams a reality.  By using his experience and knowledge of the insurance and investment industries, he helps clients work toward their financial goals. 



Mike lives in Birmingham with his wife of 30 years, Mary.  They have two adult children.  Mike is an accomplished marathon runner, and has completed 18 marathons.
To schedule a time to discuss your financial future and the possible role of insurance or investments in your financial strategy, contact us at info@allianceplanning.net or call us at (205) 968-3800 today!


